beauty and ugliness?
The image of "snake" overlaps with the beautiful girls of Kazuo Baizu's work (Magmics) - Yahoo!News
Is the mysterious beauty in common with the expression of shadows?
Since the 1950s, many works have been sent to the world.In August 2019, "Baizu Kazuo Bijo Collection" (Genkosha) was released, which focuses on beautiful girls drawn by Kazuo Baizu, who is known as the leading figure of "Fear Manga."
When I look at it with my hands, I notice the correlation between "beauty" and "fear" of Kazuo Baizu's work again.
[Image] Is it attractive because there is a shadow?
Five beautiful girls of Kazuo Baizu's work
In the preface of the Bijo Collection, there was a sentence that "fear, ugliness, shocking scenes and developments of the story stand out only when there is the beauty of the girls who are opposite," but it may be more "fear" because there is a contrast such as the beautiful face is distorted and the expression of resentment that dwells in resentment ...
There is a keyword "snake" in what appears many in Baizu Kazuo's work, but there are various ways to receive snakes, such as being perceived as "a creepy creature" by the viewer, or someone who feels "beautiful."
Some people like reptiles in the world, and others don't like them.
In this way, depending on the sensitivity of the viewer, "beauty" and "ugly" may be "snake" creatures that are united in the front and back.
This creature has been worshiped as a spiritual creature since ancient times, and it is said that the house where "white snake" lived is good luck.
There are "Hebi Girl" and "Later Girl" in the 1965 series "Mama ga Kowai!."
In general, it is a beautiful woman with a shadow that becomes a "hebijo."
If you put it in an imaginative way, can you say it is a "cool beauty" type ... ... I feel that it is the commonality of the beautiful girls appearing in Baizu works.
Among them, "Orochi," the main character of "Orochi," which was serialized in "Weekly Shonen Sunday" from 1969, is a beautiful girl character that can be said to be the representative of Baizu work, but in order to keep eternal life and eternal youth, deep sleep every 100 years, the part with strange power is reminiscent of "snake."
